KB_ID: jadedrose_brand_about
TYPE: brand
TITLE: About Jaded Rose
TAGS: about, brand, who, what, fashion, women, womenswear, london, paris, ethical, sustainable, clothing
SOURCE: brand.md
VERSION: 2026-03-09
PARENT_ID: none
TEXT:
Welcome to Jaded Rose! - the cutting-edge women's fashion brand that delivers statement styles for the fashion-forward and conscious consumer. We are an ambitious young brand and Inspired by the chic fashion hubs of Paris and London, we infuse the latest runway trends with our own artistic twist, catering to the demands of the commercial market.

We believe in fashion that's not only glamorous but also ethical. Our manufacturing processes are highly regulated to ensure that we provide top-quality garments made sustainably and ethically. We are committed to driving sustainability in the fashion industry, one garment at a time.

Our collection of clothing and accessories is designed to make you stand out in a crowd, effortlessly. From dresses and jumpsuits to skirts and trousers, our clothing range is diverse, catering to every body type and personality. Each piece in our collection is crafted with keen attention to detail to ensure that you look and feel fabulous.

We are passionate about providing a unique and edgy shopping experience to our customers, and our collections are always updated with the latest trends. Our aim is to make sure that every piece we offer leaves a lasting impression, so you can make a bold fashion statement and express your individuality.

We also understand that fashion is more than just following the latest trends; it's about making a statement and expressing your inner persona. Our brand encourages women to embrace their individuality and stand out with confidence. We aim to provide every woman with an opportunity to express herself through fashion.
--- KB_CHUNK_END ---

KB_ID: jadedrose_brand_sustainability
TYPE: brand
TITLE: Sustainability commitment
TAGS: sustainability, slow fashion, ethical, environment, limited quantities, restock, london, boutique, overproduction
SOURCE: brand.md
VERSION: 2026-03-09
PARENT_ID: none
TEXT:
At Jaded Rose, we believe in crafting beautiful garments that work for you. We are dedicated to making a positive impact and committed to developing conscious practices that honour the environment, as we grow.

As a boutique brand based in the heart of London, we understand all too well the struggles of balancing accessibility for our community while maintaining a minimal footprint.

One way we do this, is by practicing slow fashion - producing each of our styles in very limited quantities. This approach means that we minimise overproduction, and it allows us to focus on limited pieces that can be loved for a long time.

By producing fewer items in each collection, we can ensure that every piece we create has purpose, prioritising quality over quantity.

Don't worry, when we drop a popular style, we value all feedback and measure the interest before we plan our restocks. That dress you missed out on may be back very soon. If you have any queries about our restocks, feel free to email our team at hello@jadedrose.co.uk
--- KB_CHUNK_END ---
